{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC12_KYL_030.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2f,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hello, Mix Master. I dropped by to eat something."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Ayesha, it's you. I was just thinking about you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I was wondering when the that pretty apothecary was gonna come back to my tavern..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "...Oh shoot! I got fired so many times for doing this back in my underling days."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Using pick-up lines while working is strictly forbidden! That's a basic rule of this business!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x112,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Anyways, I'm happy the taste of our food here was to your liking!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Even so...you sure have lots of stuff. It's like you're moving a mountain."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Do you always travel with so much luggage on your cow?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yes.<CR>...Is that weird?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa8,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I wouldn't say it's weird as much as it's amazing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xaa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It's like you've packed your whole house..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Now that you mention it...you could be right..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Allll right, I'll prepare some tasty food for ya! You must be tired from carrying all that stuff around..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I'll treat that cow of yours to some delicious water, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Wow, thank you so much! Hehehe, I'm actually really hungry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Well, whattaya wanna eat today? I'll put my best efforts into making whatever you want!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Well, let's see... I'm leaning toward the \"Mix Master's Special of the Day\" that you listed in front of the store."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Excellent! I'll show you that calling it special isn't an exaggeration!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I'm stuffed.<CR>I think I ate too much..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I like girls who can eat a lot. I think I'm about to fall in love with you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Oh, stop teasing me.<CR>You're embarrassing me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I'm just praising you. It's not good to overeat, but there's nothing wrong with eating a lot."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Obsessing too much about your weight or figure isn't very attractive in my opinion..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "But I think every girl worries about that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa6,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, but you're totally okay, Ayesha! Girls are more attractive when they have some curves!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x39,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Y-You think so? It's gonna take me a bit of courage for me to agree with you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Well, you should stay here for a while. It's not good to move around too much right after you eat."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Okay! If you say so, I don't mind if I do!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Here ya go! Some fine ale for you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x0,
            "voice_id": 0x222,
            "name_id": 0x41,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, I gotta drink one of these every time I come to town."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "(Oh, that's alcohol... I wonder if it tastes any good...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Oh yeah, so getting back to the story, what's in all that luggage you brought with you out front?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "They're tools I use to synthesize medicine. Like my synthesis cauldron, materials to make the medicine..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Other materials that I might need... Oh, and a spare cauldron, and the spare's spare cauldron..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, do you really need all those things? Especially the latter half of that list?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "And shouldn't you limit the amount of stuff you take on a journey?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "You're probably right, but I'd feel so insecure if I didn't bring them along with me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x10f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Heh, it's more like you moved out than went on a journey..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x112,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "All right then! Please allow Mr. Kyle to lend you a helping hand!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "This place used to be part of an inn, but the rooms are all vacant now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "I'll let you use whichever room you want, so you should leave your extra stuff here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Huh, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x17f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Watching you makes me worry..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "Besides, they're vacant rooms to begin with. There shouldn't be any problems with you using one."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "In return, just come here to eat food from time to time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "If you say so, maybe I'll take up on that offer..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can now access the Crow's Room."
        }
    ]
}